<h3 id="foundations">Foundations</h3>

<p>The logo needed to embody the new brand personality, work as a standalone logo, but not detract too much when in the presence of individual products. Every letter leans up and to the right, signalling progress and momentum. The profile of the A is also mirrored by the M, to create a sense of symmetry and rhythm.</p>

