            <p class="description">To maximise our limited resources while still supporting a wide range of brand assets, I wrote a Brand Book. To contextualise the ‚Äúhow‚Äù of templates with the ‚Äúwhy‚Äù behind our decisions. Enabling teams to work with the new brand quickly, while ensuring good design outcomes. </p>
        </div>
